 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
      41pt;color:#244061'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:16.0pt'>適應症</span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#C00000'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>左主冠狀動脈（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Left main
       coronary artery, LM</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:
       "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）阻塞大於</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>50%</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#C00000'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>近端左前降支（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>LAD</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）狹窄超過</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> 70%</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>，合併兩條或三條血管病變（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>2 or
       3-vessel disease</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#C00000'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>有症狀（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>symptomatic</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）的兩條或三條血管病變</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#C00000'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>在最大劑量藥物治療下仍無法控制的嚴重心絞痛</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#C00000'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>左心室功能不良（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Ejection
       fraction &lt;0.5</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>），但存在可恢復功能的心肌（經血流重建後可改善）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>心肌梗塞後心絞痛</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> </span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>只要符合就做</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
       font-size:11.0pt'>CABG</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>，因</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
       11.0pt'>CABG</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>預後較好。</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
        5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#F79646'><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>除了</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> 1-2
        vessel disease </span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>和</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:
        Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> distal LAD occulsion</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>，</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;
        font-size:11.0pt'>PCI </span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:
        "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>預後比較好</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
       5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:#366092'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:14.0pt'>緊急冠狀動脈繞道手術的適應症</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
        5pt;margin-bottom:5pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>非</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
        11.0pt'>ST</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>段上升型心肌梗塞（</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
        font-size:11.0pt'>NSTEMI</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>）合併持續缺血，且對藥物治療或經皮冠狀動脈介入治療（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>PCI</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）無效</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
        5pt;margin-bottom:5pt' lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
        font-size:11.0pt'>ST</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>段上升型心肌梗塞（</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
        font-size:11.0pt'>STEMI</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
        11.0pt'> </span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>對所有非手術治療反應不佳</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>在</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> STEMI </span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>發作後出現持續性缺血、創傷性併發症或血管閉塞風險增加，例如</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>PCI </span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>失敗或曾接受</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> CABG </span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>的病人</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>禁忌症</span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>沒有絕對禁忌</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>相對禁忌</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#F79646'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>無症狀，且心肌梗塞或死亡機率低</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#F79646'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>合併慢性阻塞性肺病（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>COPD</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>）、肺高壓、全身性疾病</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#F79646'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>高齡</span></li>
    <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>雖然年齡並非進行</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> CABG </span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>的禁忌症，但由於高齡患者較容易出現手術併發症</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>較新的研究顯示，</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>80 </span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>歲以上患者在接受</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> CABG </span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>後，其健康相關生活品質（</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>HRQoL</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）會有所改善</span></li>
    </ul>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061'>CABG Mortality
      Risk Factor</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
