       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>、</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>2/3-vessel disease</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>、</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>LCX</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>狹窄</span></li>
